item.title: Ender 6 Expanded Frame Mounted Internal Tool Holder
item.description:
I expanded the original design by Up2no6ood to fit my needs. I also made some improvements so the wrenchs and nozzle tool were more secure.

The tool holder should be mounted just high enough that the brass brush doesn't touch the bottom, but not too high that the caliper is hard to remove without hitting the bed.

Features

Holds all the normal tools plus the following:

• Stainless steel retractable snap off blade hobby knife

• Three Harbor Freight diamond needle files (I only use 3 of the 10 normally)

• Harbor Freight 5¾ needle nose pliers

• Brass brush

• 4" adjustable wrench

• Elmers glue stick

• Tweezers or any other tall, narrow tools

If you want, you can buy me a coffee at https://ko-fi.com/vampyrex13.
item.author: vampyrex13

item.title: Rohrlfter fr Absauganlage, Tube fan for extraction system, Lfter, Absauganlage, Absaugung
item.description:
Ich habe hier einen Rohrlüfter kreiert für einen Schlauch mit 60mm Innendurchmesser und einen 120mm Lüfter.
Mit Dichtung aus TPU A95 und Wandhalterung.

Den Trichter habe ich mit 4 Wandlinien gedruckt, Stützmaterial ist nur unter den Ecken nötig.

In meinem Beispiel habe ich M4x70 Schrauben verwendet, M4x60 wären auch ok gewesen, die Länge der Schrauben richtet sich nach dem verwendeten Lüfter und deren Dicke.

Dieser Rohrlüfter ist passend für meine Absauganlage vom Creality LD-002H
https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:4869024

I have created an tube fan for a hose with 60mm inner diameter and a 120mm fan.
With seal made of TPU A95 and wall mount.

I printed the funnel with 4 wall lines, support material is only needed under the corners.

In my example I used m4x70 screws, m4x60 would be ok too, the length of the screws depends on the used fan and their thickness.

This tube fan is suitable for my Creality LD-002H exhaust system.
https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:4869024
item.author: FiliusCaliginis
